Presenter interface in cli/output/presenter.go declares one method per Result type: Todo, List, Show, DiffEdge, DiffExpanded, DiffAll, Ok, Error, Text, Version. Three implementations (PlainPresenter, ColorPresenter, JSONPresenter) each implement all methods. The Render(Presenter, Result) function dispatches a Result to the matching method via a single type-switch. See <ref spec="output.command_interface">command interface</ref>.